headline: The Cigna Group (CI) Stock Outlook Revised, Here’s What Analysts Say
summary: The Cigna Group (NYSE:CI) is among the stocks Wall Street analysts are watching closely. On November 12, Lance Wilkes, an analyst at Bernstein, trimmed the price target on The Cigna Group (NYSE:CI) to $294 from $346, while maintaining a ‘Market Perform’ rating on the stock.
